# OMEGA HARMONIC BITCOIN‚Ñ¢
## White Paper

---

## 1. Abstract

The OMEGA HARMONIC BITCOIN‚Ñ¢ project introduces a next-generation cryptographic asset platform built on original mathematical constructs, resilient cryptographic primitives, and a modular blockchain engine. It transcends the limitations of traditional proof-of-work systems by incorporating spectral prime weighting, harmonic entropy decay, and adaptive issuance curves, yielding a mathematically regulated and economically sustainable cryptocurrency architecture.

---

## 2. Introduction

Satoshi Nakamoto‚Äôs 2008 white paper defined a peer-to-peer electronic cash system. While Bitcoin revolutionized decentralized consensus, OMEGA HARMONIC BITCOIN‚Ñ¢ (OHBTC) evolves the protocol with greater cryptographic resilience, deeper mathematical formulation, and self-regulating issuance through Omega Harmonic Coin Dynamics (Œ©HCD). The system targets quantum-resistant computation, advanced multi-network operation, and optimized mining fairness without centralized mining pools.

---

